  * bzrdch.1', =>, 'dchb.1, bzrdch', =>, 'dchb, debian/install: rename
    bzrdch -> dchb;  the "dchb" string rolls off the fingertips a bit
    more smoothly;  really, this tool is an extension of dch;  reflect
    that in the name

